---
import LayoutBare from "../layouts/LayoutBare.astro";
---

<LayoutBare
  title="Imprint / Impressum · Nero Lefkada"
  description="Legal information, contact details and copyright notice for Nero Lefkada Rental&Retail."
  themeColor="#fdfbf4"
>
  <style>
    body { background: #fdfbf4; color: #0a1220; font-family: "Instrument Sans", ui-sans-serif, system-ui, sans-serif; }
    .legal-page { max-width: 680px; margin: 0 auto; padding: 6rem 2rem 4rem; }
    h1 { font-family: "Fraunces Variable", Georgia, serif; font-size: 3rem; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: -0.03em; margin-bottom: 2rem; line-height: 1.1; }
    h1 em { font-style: italic; color: #ff5a36; }
    h2 { font-family: "Fraunces Variable", Georgia, serif; font-size: 1.4rem; font-weight: 400; margin: 2.5rem 0 0.75rem; }
    p, address { font-size: 1rem; line-height: 1.8; color: #2a3a4a; margin-bottom: 1rem; font-style: normal; }
    ul { font-size: 1rem; line-height: 1.8; color: #2a3a4a; margin-bottom: 1rem; padding-left: 1.5rem; }
    li { margin-bottom: 0.4rem; }
    a { color: #00b3a7; text-decoration: none; }
    a:hover { text-decoration: underline; }
    .back { display: inline-flex; align-items: center; gap: 0.5rem; font-size: 0.8rem; letter-spacing: 0.12em; text-transform: uppercase; color: #6b7a8d; margin-bottom: 3rem; }
    .back:hover { color: #0a1220; }
    .divider { width: 40px; height: 2px; background: linear-gradient(90deg, #ff5a36, #ffc233); margin: 2rem 0; border-radius: 1px; }
    .copyright-block {
      background: #f5f3ee; border-radius: 8px; padding: 1.25rem 1.5rem;
      margin: 1.5rem 0; font-size: 0.88rem; color: #2a3a4a; line-height: 1.7;
    }
    .copyright-block strong { display: block; margin-bottom: 0.5rem; font-size: 1rem; }
    .credit-block {
      margin-top: 1rem; padding: 1rem 1.25rem; border-left: 3px solid #00b3a7;
      background: #f0f7f6; border-radius: 0 8px 8px 0; font-size: 0.88rem;
    }
  </style>

  <div class="legal-page">
    <a href="/" class="back">
      <svg width="14" height="14" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2"><path d="M19 12H5M11 5l-7 7 7 7"/></svg>
      Back to site
    </a>

    <h1>Imprint &<br><em>Legal Notice</em></h1>
    <div class="divider"></div>

    <h2>Business Details</h2>
    <address>
      <strong>Nero Lefkada Rental&amp;Retail</strong><br><br>
      Lygia Port (Λιμάνι Λυγιάς)<br>
      311 00 Lefkada (Λευκάδα), Greece (Ελλάδα)<br><br>
      <strong>Legal representative / Geschäftsführerin / Νόμιμη Εκπρόσωπος:</strong><br>
      Kristina Goldberg<br><br>
      <!-- TODO (Kristina): Wohnsitz-/Geschäftsadresse + ΑΦΜ + GEMI sobald registriert. -->
      <div style="background: #fff3e0; border-left: 3px solid #ff9933; padding: 1rem 1.25rem; margin: 1rem 0; border-radius: 0 6px 6px 0; font-size: 0.88rem; color: #5a3f14;">
        <strong>Business registration in progress.</strong><br>
        The full business address, Greek tax ID (ΑΦΜ) and commercial registry number (GEMI) are currently being finalised with the competent Greek authorities. The missing details will be published here on this page as soon as registration is complete (expected before the 2026 operating season begins on 2026-05-01).<br><br>
        <strong>Until then, if you need formal company data for invoicing or legal purposes:</strong> please contact David directly via WhatsApp <a href="https://wa.me/306955612777">+30 695 561 2777</a>. All bookings during this transition period are handled under the same Greek law (Ν. 4926/2022 personal watercraft rental) and third-party liability insurance (€700,000 per incident).
      </div>
    </address>

    <h2>Contact</h2>
    <p>
      WhatsApp: <a href="https://wa.me/306955612777">+30 695 561 2777</a> (David · Guide)<br>
      Location: Lygia Port, Lefkada, Ionian Islands, Greece<br>
      GPS: 38.7893° N, 20.7192° E
    </p>

    <h2>Operating Licence</h2>
    <p>
      Operating under Greek maritime regulations for personal watercraft rental.
      All jetskis are registered and insured in accordance with Greek Law 4926/2022
      governing recreational watercraft operations and Presidential Decree 23/2000 (water sports at sea).
    </p>

    <h2>Liability Insurance</h2>
    <p>
      Third-party liability coverage: <strong>€700,000 per incident</strong>.<br>
      Mandatory insurance pursuant to Greek Law 4926/2022 and P.D. 284/1994.<br>
      Insurance provider details available upon request.
    </p>

    <h2>Dispute Resolution</h2>
    <p>
      In the event of a dispute, Greek law applies exclusively. Jurisdiction: Courts of Lefkada, Greece.<br>
      For EU consumer disputes, the Online Dispute Resolution platform is available at:
      <a href="https://ec.europa.eu/consumers/odr" target="_blank" rel="noopener">ec.europa.eu/consumers/odr</a>
    </p>

    <h2>Copyright & Intellectual Property</h2>
    <div class="copyright-block">
      <strong>© 2026 Nero Lefkada Rental&amp;Retail · All rights reserved / Alle Rechte vorbehalten</strong>
      All texts, images, graphics, logos and other content on this website are the intellectual property of Nero Lefkada Rental&amp;Retail unless otherwise stated. Reproduction, distribution or use of any content without prior written permission is prohibited.
    </div>
    <p style="font-size: 0.88rem; color: #2a3a4a;">
      Unauthorised use of any material from this website may be subject to legal action under Greek copyright law (Ν. 2121/1993) and EU intellectual property regulations.
    </p>

    <h2>Website</h2>
    <div class="credit-block">
      <strong>Website design and development: AURA Web Studio (by Kristina Goldberg)</strong><br>
      This website was designed and developed by AURA Web Studio (owner: Kristina Goldberg) on behalf of Nero Lefkada Rental&amp;Retail.
    </div>

    <div class="divider"></div>
    <p style="font-size: 0.85rem; color: #6b7a8d;">Last updated: April 2026 · © 2026 Nero Lefkada Rental&amp;Retail</p>
  </div>
</LayoutBare>
